text: The Georgian Wikipedia is a Georgian language edition of Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia. Georgian Wikipedia started in November 2003. The Georgian Wikipedia has more than 130,000 articles.:en:List of Wikipedias#Detailed list ==Administrators and users== There are 3 administrators and more than 73,000 registered users working in Georgian Wikipedia. ==Origin of edits== * Georgian editors-91.8% * United States of America-1.6% * Others-5.6% ==Reference== ==Other websites== * Georgian Wikipedia home page Category:Wikipedias
title: Georgian Wikipedia
